@startuml uc6_export_part_1
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title UC-06 Part 1: Export Configuration và Request Submission

actor "Marketing\nAnalyst" as User
participant "Web UI\n(Next.js)" as UI
participant "Project Service\n(Golang)" as ProjectSvc
database "PostgreSQL\n(export_requests)" as DB
participant "RabbitMQ\n(export.jobs)" as MQ

== User Initiates Export ==

User -> UI: Click "Xuất báo cáo" button\n(on Dashboard UC-04)
activate UI

UI -> UI: Show Export Configuration Dialog

note over UI
  Dialog options:
  - Format: PDF / Excel / CSV
  - Date range: Full / Custom
  - Sections: Overview, Sentiment,
    Competitor, Crisis Posts
end note

UI --> User: Display configuration form
deactivate UI

== Configuration và Submission ==

User -> UI: Select options:\n- Format: PDF\n- Date: Full project range\n- Sections: All
activate UI

User -> UI: Click "Xuất báo cáo"

UI -> UI: Validate input:\n- Format selected\n- Date range valid

UI -> ProjectSvc: POST /api/v1/projects/:id/export\nAuthorization: Bearer <JWT>\n{\n  "format": "pdf",\n  "date_range": "full",\n  "sections": ["overview", "sentiment", "competitor", "crisis"]\n}
activate ProjectSvc

ProjectSvc -> ProjectSvc: Verify JWT\nExtract user_id

ProjectSvc -> ProjectSvc: Verify ownership:\nproject.created_by == user_id

ProjectSvc -> ProjectSvc: Validate export config:\n- Format in [pdf, excel, csv]\n- Sections valid

== Enqueue Export Job ==

ProjectSvc -> DB: INSERT INTO export_requests\n  (id, project_id, user_id,\n   format, config, status)\nVALUES\n  (:id, :project_id, :user_id,\n   'pdf', :config, 'pending')
activate DB

DB --> ProjectSvc: 1 row inserted\nexport_request_id
deactivate DB

ProjectSvc -> MQ: PUBLISH to exchange: smap.events\nRouting key: export.requested\nPayload:\n{\n  "event_id": "uuid",\n  "event_type": "export.requested",\n  "payload": {\n    "export_request_id": "uuid",\n    "project_id": "uuid",\n    "user_id": "uuid",\n    "format": "pdf",\n    "config": {...}\n  }\n}
activate MQ

MQ --> ProjectSvc: ACK (published)
deactivate MQ

ProjectSvc --> UI: 202 Accepted\n{\n  "export_request_id": "uuid",\n  "status": "pending",\n  "message": "Export job queued"\n}
deactivate ProjectSvc

== User Feedback ==

UI -> UI: Close dialog

UI -> UI: Show toast notification:\n"Báo cáo đang được tạo,\nbạn sẽ nhận thông báo khi hoàn tất"

UI --> User: Continue using dashboard\n(non-blocking)
deactivate UI

note over User, MQ
  User can continue using the system
  while export job processes in background
end note

@enduml
